name: Black Eyed Dragon
additional_notices:
The following token has a variable tax function on the smart contract to change tax rates post deployment.
Do your own research and be careful if you are trading this token.

description.en:
What is the project about?
As BleYd we tryin Creat a web social Platform
Included allot of tools.

What makes your project unique?
Started with the SoulTrust Dao,
A Place where people can earn Badges(non-transferable nfts) and earn Reputation Points by events. 

Events will be discussed and planned out at the Voting Platform of the Dao.

Long story short, a Fully decentralized social platform where people create everything together and get recognized by their wallets and acts

History of your project.
We made stakepools, Predict ai usefull tool, allot of events giveaways has been done. Busy with Voting Platform.

What’s next for your project?
Creating enough usefull tools together with the community to make the SoulTrust Dao,
Its all about Wallets,profile, hystory and reputation.

What can your token be used for?
To participate SoulTrust Dao
